For example ...

Here Are Just A Few Of The Ways Your Next SAAS A.I. Inbox

Can Help Your Subscribers Sell Even More!

  • If someone starts to order but doesn't, Your A.I. Inbox can alert Your users, send them a text, and allow them to have a two-way text conversation with the buyer right there in the Inbox itself. (They never have to leave your RainMakerAI.)

  • If your customer gets a DM from their prospects, Your SAAS A.I. Inbox can get the number and email of their prospect, and allow them to start a two-way conversation on any (or ALL) of those channels buith right-in for them ...right there in the Inbox.

  • If someone visits their sales page, Your A.I. Inbox can email, call, or text their Visitor for them to ask if their customers had any questions. When they reply, your users would see the reply right there in the Inbox and they can start selling directly.

  • Let's say your users send an email out that says "Open This If You're On The Fence". Your A.I. Inbox can track everyone who opens your users email and then reach out to them with an offer to answer questions over email, chat, messenger, or phone. All of their replies would be brought right there in your users Inbox so everything is organized and super-simple. (This one tactic alone is a game-changer.)

  • If someone visits your users' scheduling page but doesn't book a call, Your A.I. Inbox can reach out to their visitors by text, email, phone, or messenger and give your users' visitors the chance to help them, find a better time (or just close them right there on the spot!)

  • Your Next SAAS is buith so If someone watches your subscribers webinar but doesn't buy, your A.I. Inbox can reach out to their visitors/webinar audience to ask them if they have questions or need help.

  • You're customers would be able to have complete two-way conversations across multiple channels ...in REAL TIME ...all from your Next SAAS' Inbox.
